divs: Sighting Details I was looking up in the sky one morning while I was doing some work outside at a house by mine and I looked up and saw this weird contrail from a jet. I decided to try out my new camera and take several pics of the contrail. Later that day I went home and zoomed in and noticed there was an object next to the contrail in one of the pics.
